    <item>
      <title>行业报告指出美国库存下降，石油价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于行业报告指出美国原油库存减少，抵消了欧佩克摇摆不定的减产，油价在连续四天下跌后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 23:29:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 获胜，阿根廷完成 500 亿美元债务互换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/argentina-swaps-50-billion-of-local-debt-to-push-out-repayments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷成功地将今年到期的约 77% 比索债务换成较长期票据，这为哈维尔·米莱总统赢得了胜利，因为他积极采取行动支撑公共财政并稳定容易发生危机的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/argentina-swaps-50-billion-of-local-debt-to-push-out-repayments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 22:44:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
